            "content": "<div class=\"row center-xs middle-xs\">\n\n<div class=\"col-xs-12\">\n\nI love this product so so much! It makes my skin so glowy and even – I feel so confident when wearing it.\n\n<hr style=\"width: 20%; border: 1px solid black; text-align:center; margin-top:15px;\">\n\n<div style=\"padding-top:10px; font-weight:500;\">ABBIE</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>",
