            "content": "<div class=\"row center-xs middle-xs\">\n\n<div class=\"col-xs-12\">\n\nSince switching to the Glow Baby line my skin is more beautiful than ever. I have received more compliments on my skin in the last year than I have my entire life!\n\n<hr style=\"width: 20%; border: 1px solid black; text-align:center; margin-top:15px;\">\n\n<div style=\"padding-top:10px; font-weight:500;\">CARA B</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>",
